    <item>
      <title>All expansions come to the Test Server!</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&amp;message.id=303#M303</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"&gt;In addition to the other nifty bonuses for playing on the Test server, now anyone playing on Test can also experience all the expansions as well!&amp;nbsp; Simply download all the expansion files by making sure you have all expansions checked when you log into Test and you will be able to experience the entire game.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"&gt;This benefit to all Test server players is in addition to:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp; - Double XP&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp; - Ability to test buff your character to 25&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp; - All Veteran Rewards regardless of account eligibility&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp; - Need only one flagged raid member to enter a flagged area&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"&gt;The bonus access to the expansions while on Test will not give you access to all the expansions on Live servers though.&amp;nbsp; You will still be required to purchase any expansion you wish to use on a regular Live server.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"&gt;Come on by Test and check it out!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;FONT color=#999999&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" &gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
